general.company: Jiangsu Nonghua Intelligent Agriculture Technology Co Ltd
general.desc: Jiangsu Nonghua Intelligent Agriculture Technology Co Ltd a power equipment company, researches, develops, produces, and sells agricultural machinery in China. The products offered by the company are divided into five major segments which include Single-cylinder diesel engine segment, Multi-cylinder diesel engine segment, Agricultural equipment sector, Casting plate and General gasoline engine segment. Geographically, it operates through China however it sells the products in more than 70 countries and regions around the world.
general.short_desc: Jiangsu Nonghua Intelligent Agriculture Technology Co Ltd manufactures agricultural equipments.
